Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是土星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有光環
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用肉眼也能清晰地看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}處女座的α星 是處女座中最亮的恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是處女座的α星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本也被叫做珍珠星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍珠星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看起來薄薄的一層是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很薄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在飯能 街上有燈光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你討厭螢火蟲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 葵 日向 要不要去看螢火蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個能看到很多螢火蟲的絕佳地點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很…很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候喜歡螢火蟲喜歡到想要變成螢火蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想變成螢火蟲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像是心夏會做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽經常帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲和星空 閃閃發光 就像漂浮在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 日向 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:02:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也聯繫下楓同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待能看到螢火蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.12,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(658,206)}不可思議的螢火蟲物語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家決定一起穿著浴衣去看螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是在名栗湖那邊 媽媽你有浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有是有 可能有點大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完飯穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 葵小時候也在名栗湖那看過一次螢火蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得是幼兒園的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們家和日向家一起去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲嗎 好像模模糊糊的能想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 去那邊看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有螢火蟲妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是跟夢混淆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西怎麼可能存在啊 日向真是個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會被嘲笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她連我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和日向走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向哭得很厲害呢 一發不可收拾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次逗逗她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 那時候葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 是妖精小姐帶我們來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲妖精小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是看到了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 不要哭 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了 那時確實是有螢火蟲妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精？那種東西怎麼可能會有啊 真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會被她這樣嘲笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是這種人 還是別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人靠衣裝 葵靠浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句話我原封不動的還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說以前去看螢火蟲的時候 你哭得很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵你記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是聽媽媽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是不記得螢火蟲妖怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不記得螢火蟲妖精了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵和日向都很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是媽媽的舊衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏那件浴衣是哪來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這是我自己縫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從以前開始 媽媽就給我做了很多衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也學著她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}各位 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 楓…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 大家真有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打電話告訴你要穿浴衣集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要在意 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯能還有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是欣賞螢火蟲的絕佳地點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候來的地方大概是這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人變得相當多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去人少一點的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢變黑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣氛感覺就算出現什麼也不會奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵以前也看見過的吧 螢火蟲妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見的是螢火蟲妖精吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嗎 哪裏會有妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 妖怪才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 上面 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上有螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在宇宙一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在星海中遨遊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這麼美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現什麼也不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家回家的時候小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買便當了 來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃閃的非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽一起去就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊 有工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得是在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你還記得嗎
